{"tha-ap147:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap147:0.2":"Chattavagga ","tha-ap147:0.3":"5 Umapupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap147:1.1":"“Nibbute lokamahite, ","tha-ap147:1.2":"ahutinam patiggahe; ","tha-ap147:1.3":"Siddhatthamhi bhagavati, ","tha-ap147:1.4":"mahathupamaho ahu. ","tha-ap147:2.1":"Mahe pavattamanamhi, ","tha-ap147:2.2":"siddhatthassa mahesino; ","tha-ap147:2.3":"Umapuppham gahetvana, ","tha-ap147:2.4":"thupamhi abhiropayim. ","tha-ap147:3.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap147:3.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap147:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap147:3.4":"thupapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap147:4.1":"Ito ca navame kappe, ","tha-ap147:4.2":"somadevasanamaka; ","tha-ap147:4.3":"Pancasitisu rajano, ","tha-ap147:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap147:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap147:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap147:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap147:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma umapupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap147:7.1":"Umapupphiyattherassapadanam pancamam. "}